    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>B站个人空间: Herry013</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基于虚幻五引擎开发</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>详细介绍：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >少年方太平因一场意外，穿越回大燕建安年间。这个世界此时正处于灵气复苏之际，灵气的弥漫带来了更多的生机与希望，但同时也涌现了各种诡谲危险。在此间存活，努力求生，回到现世，是其最终目标。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏内容：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5张精美写实的古风地图 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种天气变化：晴，雨，雾，尘，雪 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4种武器类型及相应动作模组 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+武学心法 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+各具特色的敌人 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >150+武功招式卡牌 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各色NPC和各种店铺 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种主线支线任务穿插 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏场景：</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205840/extras/1c31c8dda31fb77be35aa31a1a103e10.avif?t=1755248340\" width=600 height=400 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205840/extras/6c446532aba3563749d9dd7dd2652746.avif?t=1755248340\" width=600 height=400 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205840/extras/49876424ba0fa31cc93c959b9351b161.avif?t=1755248340\" width=600 height=400 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205840/extras/2d97c6ad7c871d186535fdbd95207094.avif?t=1755248340\" width=600 height=400 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205840/extras/003699c3dd579bdee1b572f0b08ae6c1.avif?t=1755248340\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p>",
